Given an array arr[] of integers, sort the array in descending order, driver code will print arr to verify the solution.

SOURCE CODE:

class Solution {
  public:
    void sortInDesc(vector<int>& arr) {
        sort(arr.rbegin(),arr.rend());
    }
};

OUTPUTS:

Examples :

Input: arr = [324, 5, 2, 2]
Output: 324 5 2 2

Input: arr = [54, 43, 2, 1, 5]
Output: 54 43 5 2 1
